data.description: The quality craftsmanship on this spacious home is difficult to find for today's homebuyer. Built with rich materials and boasting over 4400 square feet of living space, this 6 bedroom, 3 bathroom home provides the opportunity of a lifetime at this price-  Reduced drastically to allow for the next homeowner's customization. New paint, new flooring? Buy this home and you can decide! Practical amenities include: 2 fireplaces, 3 storage rooms, 2 laundry rooms, 2 water heaters, central A/C, solid brick exterior, 3-car garage, large covered patio and a new roof- installed in 2021. This exceptional house, in such an exclusive location, is ready for you to come and make it your own!
